                <span class='font-bold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400'>₹35,000</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class='mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white'>5-Day Tamil Nadu Temple Circuit</h3>
            <p class='mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300'>
                Explore ancient temples, hill stations, and cultural heritage of Tamil Nadu.
            </p>
            <div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
                <span class='text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400'>5 days • 2-6 people</span>
                <a
                    href='/packages/tamil-nadu-5-day-temple-circuit-hill-stations'
